{"id":467,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":69,"title":"69. Traffic Rules (2)","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":11,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2.467/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/0-69-traffic-rules-2.mp3","transcript":"Excuse me. May I see your licence?\nI'm afraid I've left it at home.\nIn that case, you'll have to take it to the police station within five days.\nBut why?\nYou were speeding, ma'am.\nBut I was only doing 75!\nThere's a 70km/h speed limit on this road, ma'am.\nIs there? I didn't see a sign...\nWell, ma'am. We've been following you.\nSo you were doing 75, too.\nNo, ma'am. We were doing 90km/h... and we couldn't catch you!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:57","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Excuse me. May I see your licence?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/1.mp3","time_start":3.27,"time_end":5.87},{"position":2,"content":"I'm afraid I've left it at home.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/2.mp3","time_start":5.87,"time_end":7.88},{"position":3,"content":"In that case, you'll have to take it to the police station within five days.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/3.mp3","time_start":7.98,"time_end":11.84},{"position":4,"content":"But why?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/4.mp3","time_start":12.12,"time_end":13.16},{"position":5,"content":"You were speeding, ma'am.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/5.mp3","time_start":13.23,"time_end":14.48},{"position":6,"content":"But I was only doing 75!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/6-2022-03-10-09-45-35.mp3","time_start":14.4,"time_end":16.48},{"position":7,"content":"There's a 70km/h speed limit on this road, ma'am.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/7.mp3","time_start":16.55,"time_end":19.47},{"position":8,"content":"Is there? I didn't see a sign...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/8.mp3","time_start":19.47,"time_end":21.65},{"position":9,"content":"Well, ma'am. We've been following you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/9.mp3","time_start":21.65,"time_end":24.02},{"position":10,"content":"So you were doing 75, too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/10.mp3","time_start":24.02,"time_end":26.6},{"position":11,"content":"No, ma'am. We were doing 90km/h... and we couldn't catch you!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/69-traffic-rules-2-2022-03-07-21-27-31/11.mp3","time_start":26.75,"time_end":31.24}]}